## Usage Patterns

### Basic Usage

```tsx
() => {
  const [showChip, setShowChip] = useState(true);
  const handleClose = () => setShowChip(false);

  return (
    <div className={styles.exampleChip}>
      {showChip ? (
        <Chip
          header="Job attributes"
          selectionLabels={['Location']}
          onClose={handleClose}
        />
      ) : (
        <Button onClick={() => setShowChip(true)}>Reset</Button>
      )}
    </div>
  );
}
```

### With Long Selection Label

```tsx
() => {
  const [showChip, setShowChip] = useState(true);
  const handleClose = () => setShowChip(false);

  return (
    <div className={styles.exampleChip}>
      {showChip ? (
        <Chip
          header="Long label"
          selectionLabels={[
            'A really long selection label that gets truncated'
          ]}
          onClose={handleClose}
        />
      ) : (
        <Button onClick={() => setShowChip(true)}>Reset</Button>
      )}
    </div>
  );
}
```

